#nstall libpq-dev If you get the following error while running rails 4 after installing posgtres for the first time:
An error occurred while installing pg (0.18.3), and Bundler cannot continue.
Make sure that `gem install pg -v '0.18.3'` succeeds before bundling.

You may need to execute the following commands

sudo apt-get install libpq-dev

gem install pg

#See here:

http://stackoverflow.com/a/20754173/499167


# update for centos 
yum install postgresql-devel
